<translation id="2580436639406015883">Ukwehliswa kogaxekile nokukhwabanisa kuncike kumathokheni esimo esiyimfihlo ukusiza amasayithi alwe nokukhwabanisa futhi ahlukanise ama-bot kubantu.

Ngokusekelwe ekusebenzelaneni kwakho nesayithi, njengokungena njalo ku-akhawunti, lelo sayithi lingakhipha ithokheni yesimo esiyimfihlo kubhrawuza yakho. Kamuva, uma amanye amasayithi owavakashelayo ehlola futhi ethola ithokheni yesimo esiimfihlo esivumelekile, maningi amathuba okuthi akuphathe njengomuntu hhayi i-bot.

Amathokheni esimo esiyimfihlo athuthukisa ubumfihlo kuwebhu futhi awakwazi ukusetshenziselwa ukuthola ukuthi ungubani.</translation>
