<translation id="8765470054473112089">Uma uthayipha ibha yekheli noma ibhokisi losesho, i-Chrome ithumela lokho okuthayiphayo kunjini yakho yosesho yokuzenzakalelayo ukuze uthole iziphakamiso ezingcono. Lokhu kuvaliwe ku-Incognito.</translation>
